        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特股份回購難以撼動空頭 做空押注持續上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:泡泡瑪特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/泡泡瑪特\">泡泡瑪特</a>近兩年來的首次股票回購行動未能動搖空頭的信心，即便股價出現急劇反彈，使得這些頭寸的風險越來越大，空頭也依然不為所動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據標普全球最新數據，截至周三泡泡瑪特的空頭頭寸占自由流通股的比例約8%，高於一周前的6%。當前空頭押注已達到2023年7月以來最高水平。此前泡泡瑪特股價創下5個月來最大漲幅，公司為提振遭遇重挫的股價，採取了強有力的股票回購措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特試圖重振投資者信心的同時，相當一部分交易員對其長期發展前景持續存疑，而當前市場格局的分化，凸顯雙方的博弈日益加劇。多頭強調新品推出以及具有吸引力的估值水平，而空頭則越來越關注海外關鍵市場需求降溫的跡象。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-865733f9-1fa4-3c45-a8ae-2f92204d199b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美國市場仍持續產生相當規模的空頭倉位，當地銷售趨勢在1月繼續放緩，」Bernstein亞洲消費股分析師Melinda Hu表示。「而本周的股價反彈並非由基本面因素推動，我懷疑他們可能藉機進一步加倉。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5Gu7AczpRHoPerG9iJ07MA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/006ed8d3ce11d7f1a028a9b9ef34c838\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球數據顯示，截至周三泡泡瑪特的空頭頭寸約為6000萬股，高於一周前的4400萬股。泡泡瑪特暫未對此置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Pop Mart Short Bets Keep Rising in Defiance of Buyback Rally (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Lulu Shen.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%91%AA%E7%89%B9%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%92%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%A9%BA%E9%A0%AD-%E5%81%9A%E7%A9%BA%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-093756024.html",
